	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are the pinnacle of mortal skill with covert skills. You’d be famous if anyone had any idea you even existed. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Intelligence, or Charisma score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Deception, Sleight of Hand, or Stealth skill. If you are already proficient with all three, you gain an expertise die to one of your choice. Your maximum expertise die size for all three of these skills is a d12.</p></li><li><p>You gain a free skill specialty for each of the Deception, Sleight of Hand, and Stealth skills. They do not count against your skill specialties known.</p></li><li><p>You learn an additional combat maneuver from the combat tradition you selected from the Escroc feat.</p></li><li><p>Your Footpad follower becomes Expert.</p></li></ul><p>Once you have selected this feat, you can no longer gain levels in classes other than rogue.</p>",
